flowchart LR
  subgraph NX[Archive-Nexus - Manufacturing Event Source]
    NXR[Factory A/B/C Runtime]
    NXO[Nexus Outbox]
    NXR --> NXO
    NXO --> NXRTRY[Retry / last_error]
  end

  subgraph LG[Archive-Logistics - Route / ETA / Cost Calculator]
    LGI[Nexus Event Ingestion]
    LGR[Route + ETA Calculator]
    LGO[Logistics Outbox]
    LGI --> LGR --> LGO
  end

  subgraph LD[Archive-Ledger - Transaction / Ledger / Settlement / Reconciliation]
    LDI[Event Receiver]
    LDT[Transaction Normalizer]
    LDL[Ledger Entry Generator]
    LDS[Settlement + Reconciliation]
    LDI --> LDT --> LDL --> LDS
  end

  subgraph OS[ArchiveOS - Control Tower / Approval / Evidence / Audit]
    OSR[Ecosystem Registry]
    OSH[Health Aggregator]
    OSA[External Approval Gateway]
    OSE[Policy Evidence / Fallback Evidence]
    OSC[Callback Outbox]
    OSA --> OSE --> OSC
    OSR --> OSH
  end

  NXO -->|Logistics events| LGI
  NXO -->|Cost / settlement events| LDI
  LGO -->|Finalized logistics cost event| LDI
  LDT -->|APPROVAL_REQUIRED| OSA
  OSC -->|approve / reject callback| LDT
  OSH -. polls .-> NXO
  OSH -. polls .-> LGI
  OSH -. polls .-> LDI

  Safe[Safe-mode / dry-run] -. guards external writes .-> NXO
  Safe -. guards callbacks .-> OSC
  Iso[DEGRADED / UNAVAILABLE isolation] -. prevents failure propagation .-> OSH

